import React from 'react';
import './Login.css'

export default function Login() {
    return ( <
        div className = "login-wrapper" >
        <
        h1 > LoginID < /h1> <
        form >
        <
        label >
        <
        input type = "text"
        placeholder = "Username" / >
        <
        /label> <
        label >
        <
        p > <
        input type = "password"
        placeholder = " ******" / > < /p> < /
        label > <
        div > < p >
        <
        button type = "submit" > LOGIN < /button> </p > < /
        div > <
        /form> < /
        div >
    )
}
